tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE camera_inventory (
    camera_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(50),
    model VARCHAR(50),
    resolution VARCHAR(20),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE lens_inventory (
    lens_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(50),
    focal_length VARCHAR(20),
    max_aperture VARCHAR(10),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    quantity INT
);

  camera_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
